H. No. 1663 / 55 OG No. 39, 8257 (September 28, 1959)

[ REPUBLIC ACT NO. 2556, June 21, 1959 ]

AN ACT CREATING CERTAIN BARRIOS IN THE MUNICIPALITY OF SAMAL, PROVINCE OF DAVAO.

Be it enacted by the Senate and House of Representatives of the Philippines in Congress assembled:

SECTION 1. The following places in the Municipality of Samal, Province of Davao, are constituted as barrios of said municipality, to wit:

Anunang as Barrio Anunang;

Aumbay as Barrio Aumbay;

Aundanao as Barrio Aundanao;

Dadatan as Barrio Dadatan;

Del Monte as Barrio Del Monte;

Guilon as Barrio Guilon;

Kana-an as Barrio Kana-an;

Katagman as Barrio Katagman;

Kawag as Barrio Kawag;

Libertad as Barrio Libertad;

Licup as Barrio Licup;

Limao as Barrio Limao;

Linusutan as Barrio Linusutan;

Mambago A as Barrio Mambago A;

New San Remegio as Barrio New San Remegio;

Pangubatan as Barrio Pangubatan;

San Isidro as Barrio San Isidro;

San Miguel as Barrio San Miguel;

Sion as Barrio Sion;

Sta. Cruz as Barrio Sta. Cruz;

Tagbaobo as Barrio Tagbaobo;

Tagbay as Barrio Tagbay;

Tagbitanag as Barrio Tagbitanag; and

x. Tagdaliao as Barrio Tagdaliao.
